title: Best of The Program | Guests: President Trump & Nic McKinley | 9/21/21
description:
President Trump joins to talk to Glenn about the drastic difference between his administration and President Biden’s administration.  Nic McKinley, the founder of DeliverFund, joins to share the story of the rescued female youth soccer team.
